<plot>All are intertwined in life and the result is the beauty that surrounds us. John and Miles discover this immutable fact as they embark upon their journey through the Southwest. Encountering all aspects of the life cycle allows the poetics of being to surface within them, creating a self-knowledge and awareness that is best expressed in the words of poets and philosophers. As their narrative enfolds so does that of the Southwest.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?007559</url></doc>
